{"content": "I need to multiply 882\u2089 \u00d7 842\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n882\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 648 + 72 + 2 = 722\u2081\u2080\n\n842\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 648 + 36 + 2 = 686\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n722 \u00d7 686 = 495,292\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n495292 \u00f7 9 = 55032 r 4\n55032 \u00f7 9 = 6114 r 6\n6114 \u00f7 9 = 679 r 3\n679 \u00f7 9 = 75 r 4\n75 \u00f7 9 = 8 r 3\n8 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 8\n\nReading from bottom to top: **834364\u2089**\n\n**Verification:**\n834364\u2089 = 8\u00d759049 + 3\u00d76561 + 4\u00d7729 + 3\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 \n= 472392 + 19683 + 2916 + 243 + 54 + 4 = 495292\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n834364", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 414}